OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fmostly dry evening with some late
OL,7,Fsunny spells, then largely clear
OL,8,Fovernight. Cloudier with the odd
OL,9,Fshower over Caithness and Sutherland.
OL,10,FLight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry start with sunny spells.
OL,13,FTurning cloudy through the morning
OL,14,Fwith rain spreading eastwards. Rain
OL,15,Fheavier in the west with northern and
OL,16,Feastern areas dry for much of the
OL,17,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
